places.name: Juma Masjid msjd
places.address: Q9CV+HXQ Juma Masjid msjd, Palakkad - Ponnani Rd, SRK Nagar, Ottapalam, Kerala 679301

featured_reviews.review_id: One of the oldest and important masjid in ottapalam. 500m away from ottapalam town and railway station. One of the oldest yathemkhana in palakkad district is near to this masjid. Masjid has it's own auditorium. Auditorium is mainly used for marriage and meetings, and it's rent is cheap when  we are comparing with other auditorium in ottapalam. Every year,  the masjid will organize prayer meetings during ramzan in it's own ground. Thousands of people will gather here during that time.

places.name: Salafi Masjid, 19th Mile
places.address: Q9CV+8VH Salafi Masjid, 19th Mile, 19th Mile, SRK Nagar, Ottapalam, Kerala 679103

featured_reviews.review_id:
This is a Salafi Masjid on the Ottapalam - Palakkad Highway. There is a Madrasa adjacent to this Masjid and QHLS[Qur'an Hadess Learning School] & CRE[Continuing Religious Education] classes and other Deeni talks are conducted frequently. There is separate section for ladies in this Masjid.

Masjid is kept very clean by the authorities and above all they are true followers and preachers of Tauheed according to the Sunnah of Prophet
